{"tid":1721383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人權法案最早可以今日朝早過","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:48:14.000Z","uid":137716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bade89ecf6fc806ea1d9837293ac146577415bb0","tid":1721383,"uid":137716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"【🇺🇸突發｜參院剛啟動「熱線」機制 六小時內無人反對即通過《法案》】<br />\n<br />\n剛剛習近平在金磚國家領導人會晤上，提出「止暴制亂是香港當前最緊迫的任務」去恐嚇香港人之際，同一時間，美國國會再度出手。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志駐華盛頓代表敖卓軒收到消息，得悉Mitch McConnell剛剛將《法案》提交參議院審議，並啟動「熱線」（hotline）機制。<br />\n<br />\n在「熱線」機制下，《法案》提交後六小時內（即香港時間星期五凌晨5點前），沒有參議員反對的話，就當作參議院一致通過，法案就會明早交到白宮處理。<br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n🗺【支持眾志國際連結眾籌】<br />\n讓香港人權民主法案遍地開花｜<a href=\"http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fintlcrowdfunding&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6xPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=49504b44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding</a>"},{"pid":"4face3ffd4da2ec05827112bcd44c4a9578a98b1","tid":1721383,"uid":287019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"被逼返工都可以一路返工一路做 <br />\n<br />\n和理非想塞地鐵又淆底既入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1711917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1711917</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33919b1ce873df1770aad6a9403158319211a808","tid":1721383,"uid":330387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"FC左未嫁...."},{"pid":"bfe9d3dd50c117aaa0853678b5c56046b6bb4cc6","tid":1721383,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:48:14.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}